values:
Dear All;

I've lied to you as much as I have lied to myself.  I do not live a happy life, which is evident by my actions.  It's not that I have a bad home - far from it.  I make my life aweful by the things I do.

Dear Friends;
I appologize now.  I do not want to take our friendships for granted.  I am selfish.  You mean more to me than you could ever know.  I live a life around you, but for myself.  It shouldn't be that way, tho.  I have taken to many liberties for granted and too many things have been abused.  I am sorry.  

Dear Family;
You are my foundation and I have let the life above crumble.  You are always there and I need you more than ever.  I never make an effort...I have to.  

Dear Musicians;
As much as music is my life, I have to fix that.  I can not only work on music and let everything else turn to shit because of it.  I have to start saying no.  

From October 31st to last night, I had not been drunk.  Last night, I got obliterated with my friends watching.  I don't know why.  I was mad at my mother, and I just wanted it to go away.  Doing close to 15 shots of Vodka doesn't make anything go away.  It makes you black out, which I did.  I don't even remember them leaving or talking to my mother.  WHY?  FUCKING WHY DID I DO THAT?  I embaressed myself infront of the people I care about.  To you I am incredibly sorry.  

I am letting my father take the car for the week, probably over the weekend and til next monday.  I am going to downright STOP Drinking until graduation.  I can't do it anymore.  I always do dumb, DUMB things when I do.  I have to go to school.  I have to get there ontime and be present all day.  I need to graduate.  I want music to be the rest of my life, not beer and cigerettes.  

As far as sex goes...if you've had it with me, great.  I am not a whore, but I can't do it like this anymore.  I want the right person.  Not the person for right-now.  

Before you ask, I am not quitting smoking yet.  

I have made these resolutions.  I will adhere.
